query:
SELECT 
            COUNT(*) as count
        FROM  
            original_videos ov
        INNER JOIN 
            videos v 
        ON 
            v.original_video_id = ov.id
        WHERE 
            ov.id = $1 
            AND 
            (v.stage != 'DOWNLOADING' OR v.stage != 'CUTTING' OR v.error = true)
